query:
SELECT DISTINCT ON (d.id) d.id "id: _", d.name, d.wireguard_pubkey, d.user_id, d.created FROM device d JOIN "user" u ON d.user_id = u.id JOIN group_user gu ON u.id = gu.user_id JOIN "group" g ON gu.group_id = g.id WHERE g."name" IN (SELECT * FROM UNNEST($1::text[]))
                    AND u.is_active = true
                    ORDER BY d.id ASC
